## 2ï¸âƒ£ Which Region Generates the Highest Revenue?

### ğŸ”¹ Business Objective  
To identify the strongest geographical market.

### ğŸ”¹ Theoretical Insight  
By joining Orders and Customers tables and grouping by region, we determine which region contributes the highest sales.

### ğŸ”¹ Business Impact  
- Focus marketing and expansion in high-performing regions  
