## 3ï¸âƒ£ Which Product Category is the Most Profitable?

### ğŸ”¹ Business Objective  
To identify the highest-earning product segment.

### ğŸ”¹ Theoretical Insight  
By joining Orders and Products tables and grouping by category, we determine which category generates maximum profit.

### ğŸ”¹ Business Impact  
- Invest more in high-margin categories  
- Improve pricing or cost structure of low-profit categories  
- Adjust inventory planning  
- Improve product portfolio strategy  

High sales does not always mean high profit â€” profitability matters more.

