## 4ï¸âƒ£ Who Are the Top 5 Customers by Revenue?

### ğŸ”¹ Business Objective  
To identify high-value customers.

### ğŸ”¹ Theoretical Insight  
Grouping sales by customer helps identify customers contributing the most revenue.

### ğŸ”¹ Business Impact  
- Build loyalty programs for top customers  
- Provide personalized offers  
- Reduce churn risk  
- Strengthen long-term customer relationships  

Often, a small percentage of customers generates a large portion of revenue (Pareto Principle).

